        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued May 8 at 4:58PM EDT until May 8 at 5:30PM EDT by NWS Greenville-Spartanburg SC</headline>
        <description>At 458 PM EDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 6 miles west of
Rutherfordton, moving east at 15 mph.

HAZARD...Ping pong ball size hail and 60 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...People and animals outdoors will be injured. Expect hail
damage to roofs, siding, windows, and vehicles. Expect wind
damage to trees and power lines.

Locations impacted include...
Green Hill, Rutherfordton, Spindale, Union Mills, and Forest City.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
